CityPay,is,an,online,payment,service,that,offers,a,secure,payment,gateway,enabling,merchants,to,accept,payments,from,a,range,of,environments,from,mobile,phones,and,web,browsers,through,to,fully,integrated,solutions,The,CityPay,PayPOST,API,is,RESTful,payment,API,used,for,server,to,server,transactional,processing,Merchants,can,use,the,API,to,integrate,CityPay,payment,services,into,their,own,applications,The,API,provides,a,number,of,payment,mechanisms,including,fraud,protection,preauthorization,and,Internet,MOTO,CA,transaction,processing,The,API,provides,data,in,XML,or,JSON